    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">431 Stevens street</name><ptr target="loc.06094_n1"/>
                    <name type="place">Camden New Jersey</name>
                    <name type="place">U S America</name>
                    <date when="1882-10-11">Oct 11 '82</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear Miss Ford</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>
                Yours of Sept: 25th <choice><abbr>rec'd</abbr><expan>received</expan></choice>&#8212;&amp; accordingly I send you (same mail with this&#8212;same
                address) my two volumes&#8212;poetic and prose. The price is one
                pound sterling (which includes the books, postage, &amp; everything)&#8212;send to
                me here by P. O. order<ptr target="loc.06094_n2"/>&#8212;
            </p>
            <p> 
                When you see Edward Carpenter tell him I am well &amp; hearty
                (considering) &amp; send him my love&#8212;
            </p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
    </text>
